---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="10Botics Tutor Privacy Policy | 導師應用程式私隱政策"
  description="Privacy policy and personal information collection statement for the 10Botics Tutor app."
>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-10 max-w-4xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">10Botics Tutor Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-gray-600">導師應用程式私隱政策</p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">Effective date / 生效日期：20 July 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mt-10">
      <p>
        This policy explains how 10Botics Ltd (“10Botics”, “we”, “us”) collects, uses,
        stores and protects personal data through the 10Botics Tutor mobile application
        and related tutor services. It also serves as a Personal Information Collection
        Statement under the Personal Data (Privacy) Ordinance of Hong Kong.
      </p>
      <p>
        本政策說明 10Botics Ltd（「10Botics」、「本公司」或「我們」）如何透過
        10Botics Tutor 流動應用程式及相關導師服務收集、使用、儲存及保障個人資料，
        並構成香港《個人資料（私隱）條例》下的個人資料收集聲明。
      </p>

      <h2>1. Data we collect / 我們收集的資料</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Third-party sign-in identity, including name, email address and account identifier／第三方登入身份資料，包括姓名、電郵地址及帳戶識別碼</li>
        <li>Contact and profile details, residential address and language preferences／聯絡及個人資料、住址及語言偏好</li>
        <li>Hong Kong Identity Card information and copy, recent photograph and eligibility documents／香港身份證資料及副本、近照及資格證明文件</li>
        <li>Education, qualifications, teaching experience and employment or freelancer status／教育程度、資歷、教學經驗及僱傭或自由工作者狀況</li>
        <li>Bank, payment and account-holder information used to arrange payments／用於安排付款的銀行、付款及戶口持有人資料</li>
        <li>Emergency-contact name, relationship and telephone number／緊急聯絡人的姓名、關係及電話號碼</li>
        <li>Teaching opportunities, applications, lesson assignments, attendance and agreement records／教學機會、申請、課堂安排、出席及協議紀錄</li>
        <li>Precise device location and time when a tutor performs a lesson check-in／導師進行課堂簽到時的裝置精確位置及時間</li>
        <li>Device, app version, notification token, security and technical diagnostic information／裝置、應用程式版本、通知識別碼、安全及技術診斷資料</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Why we use the data / 資料用途</h2>
      <p>We use personal data to:</p>
      <p>我們使用個人資料以：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>authenticate users and secure their accounts／驗證使用者身份及保障帳戶安全</li>
        <li>assess onboarding, eligibility and reactivation／處理登記、資格審核及重新啟用</li>
        <li>offer and administer teaching opportunities, applications and lessons／提供及管理教學機會、申請及課堂</li>
        <li>record attendance, investigate disputes and support safeguarding／記錄出席、調查爭議及支援保障工作</li>
        <li>calculate, verify and arrange payments／計算、核實及安排付款</li>
        <li>send operational, lesson and account notifications／發送營運、課堂及帳戶通知</li>
        <li>comply with contractual, tax, accounting, insurance, safeguarding and legal obligations／履行合約、稅務、會計、保險、保障及法律責任</li>
        <li>prevent fraud, abuse and unauthorised access／防止欺詐、濫用及未經授權的存取</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Whether providing data is obligatory / 是否必須提供資料</h2>
      <p>
        Fields marked as required, identity and eligibility documents, payment information
        needed for payment, and location at the time of check-in are obligatory for the
        relevant function. If they are not provided, we may be unable to complete onboarding,
        confirm eligibility, arrange payment or verify attendance. Notification permission is optional.
      </p>
      <p>
        標示為必填的欄位、身份及資格文件、付款所需資料，以及簽到時的位置資料，均為使用相關功能所必須。
        如不提供，我們可能無法完成登記、確認資格、安排付款或核實出席。通知權限則屬自願提供。
      </p>

      <h2>4. Disclosure and service providers / 披露及服務供應商</h2>
      <p>
        Personal data is accessible only where reasonably necessary. It may be disclosed to
        authorised 10Botics personnel, relevant schools or customers for lesson administration,
        professional advisers, insurers, banks or payment providers, and competent authorities
        where required by law. We also use service providers for identity verification,
        notifications, cloud hosting, storage and other functions supporting the app.
        They process data subject to contractual, technical or legal safeguards.
      </p>
      <p>
        個人資料只會在合理需要的情況下供有關人士使用，並可能披露予獲授權的 10Botics 人員、
        為管理課堂而需要資料的相關學校或客戶、專業顧問、保險公司、銀行或付款服務供應商，
        以及法律要求下的主管機關。我們亦使用提供身份驗證、通知、雲端主機、儲存及
        其他應用程式支援功能的服務供應商。
        有關資料處理受合約、技術或法律保障約束。
      </p>

      <h2>5. Cross-border processing / 跨境處理</h2>
      <p>
        Some service providers may process or store data outside Hong Kong. We take reasonable
        steps to select reputable providers and apply appropriate safeguards to such transfers.
      </p>
      <p>
        部分服務供應商可能在香港境外處理或儲存資料。我們會採取合理措施選用信譽良好的供應商，
        並為有關資料轉移採取適當保障。
      </p>

      <h2>6. Retention / 資料保留</h2>
      <p>
        We retain data for as long as reasonably necessary for tutor administration and the
        purposes described above. Agreement, payment, lesson, attendance, safeguarding,
        dispute and audit records may be retained after access is closed where necessary for
        contractual, accounting, tax, insurance, security or legal purposes. Data no longer
        required will be securely deleted or anonymised in accordance with our retention practices.
      </p>
      <p>
        我們會在合理所需期間內保留資料，以管理導師及達成上述用途。帳戶存取權關閉後，
        如為合約、會計、稅務、保險、安全或法律用途所需，本公司仍可能保留協議、付款、課堂、
        出席、保障、爭議及審計紀錄。不再需要的資料將按本公司的保留安排安全刪除或匿名化。
      </p>

      <h2>7. Security / 資料安全</h2>
      <p>
        We use reasonable administrative, access-control and technical measures to protect
        personal data. No internet or storage system can be guaranteed completely secure;
        users should protect their sign-in account and immediately report suspected misuse.
      </p>
      <p>
        我們採用合理的行政、存取控制及技術措施保障個人資料。任何互聯網或儲存系統均不能保證絕對安全；
        使用者應妥善保護其登入帳戶，並立即報告任何懷疑濫用情況。
      </p>

      <h2>8. Access, correction and account closure / 查閱、更正及關閉帳戶</h2>
      <p>
        You may request access to or correction of personal data in accordance with applicable
        law. You may also request closure of app access. Closing access retires the tutor account;
        it does not automatically erase business records that 10Botics reasonably needs to retain.
        See our <a href="/tutor-app/account-closure">Account Closure page</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        你可根據適用法律要求查閱或更正個人資料，亦可要求關閉應用程式存取權。
        關閉存取權會把導師帳戶標記為停用，但不會自動刪除 10Botics 合理需要保留的業務紀錄。
        詳情請參閱<a href="/tutor-app/account-closure">帳戶關閉頁面</a>。
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes / 政策更新</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy when the app, our practices or legal requirements change.
        The current version and effective date will be published on this page.
      </p>
      <p>
        當應用程式、我們的處理方式或法律要求有所改變時，我們可能更新本政策。
        最新版本及生效日期將於本頁公布。
      </p>

      <h2>10. Contact / 聯絡我們</h2>
      <p>
        10Botics Ltd<br />
        Email / 電郵：<a href="mailto:info@10botics.com">info@10botics.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
